Package net.dragondelve.customdriversutil.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Driver
    Represents a model of a driver with their track overrides included as described by AMS2 Developers here: Reiza AMS2Forums Stores Livery Name that is shared with its track specific overrides.
    DriverBase
    Represents a base model of a driver described by AMS2 Developers here: Reiza AMS2 Forums
    DriverLibrary
    Represents a library of drivers.
    Grid
    Full Grid of Drivers stores the specific class that has been assigned to the grid.
    OverrideFlags
    A class that encapsulates all flags that determine whether you should override the DriverBase's properties or not.
    Track
    Represents an in game track.
    TrackLibrary
    Library of tracks that is used when generating a custom AI grid.
    TrackOverride
    Represents a model of a specific track override as described by AMS2 Developers here: AMS2 Reiza Forums It stores a list of track names for which this track is an override.
    VehicleClass
    Represents an in game vehicle class.
    VehicleClassLibrary
    Represents a reference Library of Vehicle Classes.
